gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 128, Lakers 121
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Lakers, 128-121, tonight in Los Angeles. Stephen Curry led the Warriors with 31 points, six rebounds, and five assists as Klay Thompson (26 points, four rebounds, three assists) and Jonathan Kuminga (23 points, four assists) totaled 49 points. The Warriors received 47 points from their bench while the Lakers had 25. LeBron James (40 points, eight rebounds, nine assists) and DAngelo Russell (23 points, 13 assists) led the Lakers. The Warriors improve to 35-31 as the Lakers move to 36-32.
